      "text": "Democrats want to regulate every other aspect of your life, from the car you drive to your right to carry a firearm.\n\nBut for some reason, they couldn't care less about verifying voters in federal elections.\n\nReally makes you wonder. https://t.co/7TmNKqm1xV",
